headline: Huge Acquires Creative Studio, Both&Yes, to Scale Intelligent Experiences Amid Accelerated Growth
summary: NEW YORK, October 01, 2025--Huge, the independent design and technology company, has acquired Both&Yes, the creative studio credited with building next-generation digital and AI experiences for Alphabet companies Google and YouTube, as well as leading creative innovation for brands such as Robinhood, Harry’s, and Wild.xyz. The move accelerates Huge’s ability to develop future-ready intelligent experiences for the world’s most iconic brands.
